{
  "stem": "11205.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He always showed the picture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Germans came?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not many.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People used to go, you know, to overseas.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From my uncle-- actually, I had two-- two-- four cousins-- it was two sons and two daughters-- went to Brazil and to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So otherwise, people used to go, you know, to America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Though America was very hard to get, so they used to go to other countries.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Coming from Bais Yaakov, took enough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We remember-- I-- the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's when we-- we knew, and-- but it went-- the Germans came-- actually, it was a lot of people running from, you know, from the part-- that part from Poland, and they used to go to-- to-- people were evacuated, running.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know till the eighth day of-- when the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the first time we experienced a bombing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what they actually-- what happened-- because the government and all ministers, that-- they-- they passed through Chelm because a lot of Polish ministers ran away to Romania.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They gathered at the-- how [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- where the government is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and most probably, the Germans find out, and they-- but they came in to bomb.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what they bombed-- we lived like [INAUDIBLE], and the next-- next was [INAUDIBLE], which it was a station, so that's what they bombed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was our street and-- and a-- a station because they thought they-- they will still catch up with them, and they missed it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where I was?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in the back yard, and over the fence, it was a hospital, and a soldier was lying on the ground, and we were talking to him.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
